definitions.definition: A surname from Middle English , a variant of Dean .
A male given name transferred from the surname .
A suburban area in the Metropolitan Borough of Bolton , Greater Manchester , England ( OS grid ref SD6907 ) .
A small village and civil parish (served by Oakley and Deane Parish Council) in Basingstoke and Deane borough , Hampshire , England ( OS grid ref SU5450 ) .
An unincorporated community in Letcher County , Kentucky , United States .
